{"tid":2083940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國自民黨：自民黨反對會違反中英聯合聲明和損害港人公民自由的港區國安法","createTime":"2020-06-29T05:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T06:16:30.000Z","uid":70063,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3d677701c9822a0aa9f067cb2802598271832a","tid":2083940,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LibDems/status/1277227751150243841?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLibDems%2Fstatus%2F1277227751150243841%3Fs%3D19&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=c123295a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLibDems%2Fstatus%2F1277227751150243841%3Fs%3D19&h=dd38a47b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LibDems/status/1277227751150243841?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"4100ae1b53231a83b35f17abc2052cdb37a63046","tid":2083940,"uid":361247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c3d677701c9822a0aa9f067cb2802598271832a","tid":2083940,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LibDems/status/1277227751150243841?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLibDems%2Fstatus%2F1277227751150243841%3Fs%3D19&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=c123295a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLibDems%2Fstatus%2F1277227751150243841%3Fs%3D19&h=dd38a47b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LibDems/status/1277227751150243841?s=19</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"反對都無用,根本一定過<br />\n依家可以做既<strong>71維園見</strong>,plan定走難或者武裝革命"},{"pid":"5e6d7f88695b9d6208fb7c072207f2fa44da8e89","tid":2083940,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"支持LibDem，大家71見<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=6c1c05e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3c8d5d1cef8fbe3a48e9b58e44b32f8cd33ff31d","tid":2083940,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"71維園見"},{"pid":"df71e8981627e2b51b4f52910f8f961f7633070a","tid":2083940,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}